===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|pirat|e|}}
# {{internet}} To [[obtain]], usually by downloading from a [[file sharing]] [[network]], an unauthorized copy of [[software]] or other works.
#: ''Not willing to spend full price for the game, Heidi instead pirated a copy.''

===Adjective===
